Package: cuems-audioplayer
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, jackd2
Description: MTC synchronized audio player
 This is an audio player that can play in sync with MTC timecode
 and is part of the cuems project. It supports various audio formats
 including WAV, AIFF, MP3, FLAC, and can extract audio from video files.
